\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Stella P. ( Boynton Beach, FL)</span></div>\n<p>I’ve been using it for three weeks and see improvement in my skin color, softness, and radiance.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Dani D. (Seymour, TX)</span></div>\n<p>I use it twice a day as recommended but my jar barely lasts me one month</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Jane S. (San Mateo, CA</span></div>\n<p>I have been suffering from rosacea for over 12 years, my skin red and inflamed, and this helped get it under control, so I highly recommend it.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Frances T. (Rocky Hill, CT)</span></div>\n<p>I hoped this would make a bigger difference, but it didn’t. I don’t know why, the reviews from others tend to seem very good.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Valerie W. (Boulder, CO)</span></div>\n<p>My skin looks so healthy!</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\"