126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Patricia M. (Jackson, TN)</span></div>\n<p> am happy with this product, I tried other products in this line that I didn’t like but had good results with Cold Plasma. I don’t mind the smell either.</p> \n</div>","Perricone MD Cold Plasma Face & Eyes","","inherit","closed","closed","","118-revision-16","","","2010-11-15 15:23:00","2010-11-15 20:23:00","","118","http://www.skincaresearch.com/211/118-revision-16/","0","revision","","0");
