aims to work with an Ionic-Suspension Carrier.  Ions are atoms that have lost or gained electrons, making them positively or negatively charged. While other creams do contain ions that are suspended, we haven’t seen this scientific terminology used with other creams before, and have not been able to conclusively determine whether there is anything different about this or not.</p>\n<p>The only other main issue we could find with Cold Plasma is that it has a fishy smell. If you can tolerate that though, Cold Plasma does seem to work well for many people, of all ages and all skin types. It’s not greasy and it absorbs quickly, and makes a great base for makeup.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong></p>\n<p>The face cream retails at $150 an ounce, and the eye cream retails at $95 for half an ounce.  You can buy them together for $195, a $50 savings.</p>\n<p><strong>Money back guarantee:</strong></p>\n<p>Cold Plasma comes with a 45-day money back guarantee.</p>\n<p><strong>Shipping:</strong></p>\n<p>They offer free shipping on the main website.</p>\n<p><strong>Replenishment program:</strong></p>\n<p>They have an auto-ship program where you can automatically receive a replenishment every 60 days.</p>\n<p><strong>Ingredient list for face cream:</strong></p>\n<p>Water, Glycerin, Tetrahexyldecyl Ascorbate, Phosphatidylcholine, Isopropyl Palmitate, L-Tyrosine, Butylene Glycol, Glyceryl Stearate, Peg-100 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Oligopeptide-17, Ceteareth-20, Magnesium Aspartate, Zinc Gluconate, Dimethyl Mea (Dmae), Docosahexaenoic Acid, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Phenoxyethanol, Dimethicone, Caprylyl Glycol, Glycolic Acid, Retinyl Palmitate, Saccaromyces Ferment, Elaeis Guineensis (Palm) Oil, Carbomer, Disodium Edta, Tocotrienols, Copper Gluconate, Polysorbate 20, Sorbic Acid, Tocopherol, Sodium Hyaluronate, Acetyl Hexapeptide-8, Palmitoyl Oligopeptide, Astaxanthin, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-3</p>\n<p><strong>Ingredient list for eye cream:</strong></p>\n<p>Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Phosphatidylcholine, Isopropyl Palmitate, Glycerin, Tetrahexyldecyl Ascorbate, Glyceryl Stearate, Peg-100 Stearate, Docosahexaenoic Acid, Squalane, Butylene Glycol, Benzyl Alcohol, Ceteareth-20, Magnesium Aspartate, Zinc Gluconate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Disodium Edta, Farnesol, Oligopeptide-17, Elaris Guineensis (Palm) Oil, Carbomer, Copper Gluconate, Tocotrienols, Polysorbate 20, Tocopherol, Sodium Hyaluronate, Fragrance, Linalool, Palmitoyl Oligopeptide, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Most helpful Customers’ reviews</h2>\n\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Vicki T. (Wasilla, AK)</span></div>\n<p>I noticed a decrease in my brow furrows very quickly with this.</p> \n</div>\n\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Vicki T. (Wasilla, AK)</span></div>\n<p>I noticed a decrease in my brow furrows very quickly with this.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Eiko R. (Del Ray Beach, FL)</span></div>\n<p>Maecenas tincidunt nisi pulvinar sem ornare id hendrerit arcu vulputate. Sed nisi dolor, sollicitudin eget commodo eget, aliquam in lectus. Nulla consectetur egestas orci vel convallis. Mauris lacus ipsum, pellentesque id consectetur eu, suscipit in augue. Aenean porttitor, tellus at adipiscinl licitudin eget</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Gayle Y. (Newport Beach, CA)</span></div>\n<p>It’s light, goes on great, and soaks in immediately. I use it twice a day right before makeup.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Deborah R. (Aurora, CO)</span></div>\n<p>Great product. I use both the face and eye product together. I began using this because my face felt droopy and I now notice my skin is more elastic. I noticed a difference within a few days, and my friends told me the same. I don’t go a day without it now because I remember what I looked like before I began using this, and I like how I look right now much better. I would recommend this to anyone.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Diane F. (Youngaville, NC)</span></div>\n<p>Expensive but worth the cost.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Grace V. (Grand Prairie, TX)</span></div>\n<p>I noticed my skin more even and glowing in 4 days.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Terry Z. (Seaford, NY)</span></div>\n<p>The product does what it says! My skin is smoother and tighter, very happy with it!</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Stella P. ( Boynton Beach, FL)</span></div>\n<p>I’ve been using it for three weeks and see improvement in my skin color, softness, and radiance.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Dani D. (Seymour, TX)</span></div>\n<p>I use it twice a day as recommended but my jar barely lasts me one month</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Jane S. (San Mateo, CA</span></div>\n<p>I have been suffering from rosacea for over 12 years, my skin red and inflamed, and this helped get it under control, so I highly recommend it.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Frances T. (Rocky Hill, CT)</span></div>\n<p>I hoped this would make a bigger difference, but it didn’t. I don’t know why, the reviews from others tend to seem very good.</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Valerie W. (Boulder, CO)</span></div>\n<p>My skin looks so healthy!</p> \n</div>\n<div id=\"customers-review\">\n<div><img src=\"http://www.skincaresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5stars.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"5stars\" width=\"126\" height=\"17\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-97\" /> <span>Patricia M. (Jackson, TN)</span></div>\n<p> am happy with this product, I tried other products in this line that I didn’t like but had good results with Cold Plasma. I don’t mind the smell either.</p> \n</div>","Perricone MD Cold Plasma Face & Eyes","","inherit","closed","closed","","118-revision-22","","","2010-11-15 15:35:13","2010-11-15 20:35:13","","118","http://www.skincaresearch.com/217/118-revision-22/","0","revision","","0");
